data.description: Beautiful and updated 3 bd/1 bth ranch in great neighborhood in Streamwood! The moment you enter the front door you're greeted by a spacious living room with a large bay window and new vinyl flooring and trim (done in Oct 2023) that flow throughout the home. The eat-in kitchen features all SS appliances, plenty of cabinet space and sliders that lead out to your patio. There are 3 good-sized bedroom and an updated full bath. Outside, enjoy your large yard with patio, fire pit, plenty of space for gardening or entertaining and 2.5 car detached garage. Across the street from the elementary school & Shady Oaks Disc Golf, close to major roads, grocery shopping, restaurants and more - you can't beat this location. All that's left to do is move in! Easy to show, schedule your tour today!
